# SpaceEngine-2.0 (minimal)

This repository is an initial minimal skeleton for the Cosmos / SpaceEngine-2.0 project.

What you get in this branch (feature/phase0-init):
- Minimal Engine core (Engine, Timer, Application)
- Simple Logger that writes to stdout and logs/engine.log
- ConfigManager stub
- CMake build and a small console executable that runs ~3 seconds
- GitHub Actions workflow to build and run the binary on ubuntu-latest

How to build locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/GLS-dotcom/SpaceEngine-2.0.git
cd SpaceEngine-2.0
git checkout feature/phase0-init
mkdir build && cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release
cmake --build . --config Release --parallel
./bin/CosmosEngine
